### Order Service — Local Development
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7010
@contentType = application/json

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### PLACE ORDER
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Valid order — single line, product in stock
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "aabbccdd-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa1",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### 2. Valid order — multiple lines
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "aabbccdd-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa1",
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": "4fb96f75-6828-5673-b4fc-3d074f77afa2",
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

###

### 3. Out of stock product (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "aabbccdd-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "5fc07a86-7939-6784-c5ad-4e185a88bac3",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### 4. Non-existent product (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "aabbccdd-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### 5. Empty items list (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "customerId": "aabbccdd-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
  "items": []
}

